    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and has been meticulously preserved as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are absolutely no scratches, dents, or chips to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, with the leather upholstery still firm and every electronic feature functioning perfectly. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or a discerning buyer to own a vehicle that has been kept in climate-controlled storage and maintained with an open checkbook.",
